<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="de">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Frohe Weihnachten</title>
    <style>
        /* Grundlayout */
        body {
            margin: 0;
            height: 100vh;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-image: url("https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1675373420153-809b8d1da50c?q=80&w=1740&auto=format&fit=crop&ixlib=rb-4.1.0&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D");
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
        }

        /* Overlay-Box */
        .card {
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
            color: white;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 20px;
            animation: fadeIn 2s ease;
        }

        /* Titel */
        h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            animation: glow 2s infinite alternate;
        }

        /* Text */
        p {
            max-width: 400px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        /* Button mit Hover-Effekt */
        .btn {
            padding: 12px 25px;
            background-color: #c62828;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 25px;
            transition: transform 0.3s, background-color 0.3s;
        }

        .btn:hover {
            background-color: #ff5252;
            transform: scale(1.1);
        }

        /* Snowflake */
       

        .snow {
            position: absolute;
            top: -5vh;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            animation: fadeout 5s linear infinite;
        }


        /* Animationen */
        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(30px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        @keyframes glow {
            from {
                text-shadow: 0 0 5px #fff;
            }
            to {
                text-shadow: 0 0 20px #ffeb3b;
            }
        }

        @keyframes fadeout {
            from {
                transform: translateY(0);
                opacity: 1;
            }
            to {
                transform: translateY(100vh);
                opacity: 0.2;
            }


        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="card">
        <h1>Frohe Weihnachten 🎄</h1>
        <p>
            Ich wünsche dir besinnliche Feiertage, viel Freude
            und einen guten Rutsch🛝 ins neue Jahr!
        </p>
        <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dQw4w9WgXcQ&list=RDdQw4w9WgXcQ&start_radio=1" class="btn"> Mehr erfahren</a>

    </div>



    <div>
        <div class="snow" style="left:10%;">❄️</div>
        <div class="snow" style="left:30%; animation-delay: 1s; animation-duration: 4s;">❄️</div>
        <div class="snow" style="left:70%; animation-delay: 0.5s; animation-duration: 3s;">❄️</div>
        <div class="snow" style="left:90%; animation-delay: 1.5s;">❄️</div>
    </div>



</body>
</html>
